    Package {
        registry: PackageRegistry,  // npm, crates, pypi
        name: String,
        version: VersionSpec,
        source_url: String
    },

    // Generated content (methodologies, blueprints)
    Generated {
        content: String,
        generated_at: Timestamp,
        generator: String
    }
}
```

### Benefits of Reference-Based Storage

```
WHY REFERENCES?

1. NO DUPLICATION
   - Files exist once on disk
   - ZSEI stores meaning, not bytes
