2. AUTOMATIC UPDATES
   - File changes detected via hash
   - Re-index only what changed
   - Always current

3. EXTERNAL LINKING
   - Packages linked, not downloaded
   - URLs referenced, not cached
   - Context captured, not content

4. INTEGRITY
   - Hash verification on access
   - Detect external changes
   - Alert on corruption
```

